Rudolf Steiner is a relatively unknown austrian philosopher and spiritualist, who is known for his roots in education and Whardoff schools.

jj

His main beliefs where that all humans had a spiritual side which could be worked upon through relatively strict thoughtfullness and that there were different parts of our consciousness, such as our life-body, our astral realm, and etherial realm.

